&lt;h2>Class and Instance&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="class-and-instance">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#class-and-instance" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;strong>클래스(Class)&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>객체를 생성하기 위한 템플릿 또는 청사진&lt;/li>
&lt;li>관련된 속성(변수)과 메서드(함수)를 그룹화한 것&lt;/li>
&lt;li>데이터와 해당 데이터를 처리하는 메서드를 포함&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>인스턴스(Instance)&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>클래스를 기반으로 생성된 실제 객체&lt;/li>
&lt;li>클래스의 속성과 메서드를 상속받아 실제로 메모리에 할당된 것&lt;/li>
&lt;li>각 인스턴스는 고유한 속성값을 가질 수 있음&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">class&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nc">Car&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1"># 클래스 정의&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">def&lt;/span> &lt;span class="fm">__init__&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="bp">self&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">brand&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">model&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">):&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="bp">self&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">brand&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">brand&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="bp">self&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">model&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">model&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 인스턴스 생성&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">car1&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">Car&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Toyota&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Camry&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1"># car1은 Car 클래스의 인스턴스&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">car2&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">Car&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Honda&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Civic&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1"># car2는 Car 클래스의 인스턴스&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0">
